PASS: &lt;Binary test completed&gt;
INFO: &lt;BINARY:1024:1!&gt; 
PASS: &lt;Binary test completed&gt;
INFO: &lt;BINARY:512:0!&gt;
PASS: &lt;Binary test completed&gt;
... 
PASS: &lt;Binary test completed&gt;
